1
00:00:48,280 --> 00:00:53,000
[The Ferry Man: 10th Anniversary]

2
00:00:53,460 --> 00:00:56,010
[Episode 22]

3
00:01:12,070 --> 00:01:13,710
Did you see anything?

4
00:01:14,590 --> 00:01:15,200
I did.

5
00:01:15,680 --> 00:01:16,680
What do you think?

6
00:01:21,560 --> 00:01:23,310
I think the Heavenly Maiden

7
00:01:23,480 --> 00:01:24,560
is going through the Five Declines.

8
00:01:24,560 --> 00:01:26,020
Her life is coming to an end.

9
00:01:26,020 --> 00:01:27,150
Isn't that obvious?

10
00:01:27,280 --> 00:01:28,590
We finally got you here.

11
00:01:28,590 --> 00:01:30,390
Tell us something we don't know.

12
00:01:30,860 --> 00:01:32,000
You are the local Earth God,

13
00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:33,150
the only god I know.

14
00:01:34,759 --> 00:01:35,220
Well...

15
00:01:35,590 --> 00:01:36,789
Logically speaking,

16
00:01:36,789 --> 00:01:38,789
immortals have endless lifespans.

17
00:01:39,430 --> 00:01:40,310
But she...

18
00:01:41,840 --> 00:01:43,229
How did she end up like this?

19
00:01:43,229 --> 00:01:44,930
You're asking me? Who should I ask?

20
00:01:44,930 --> 00:01:46,229
How did she end up like this?

21
00:01:46,229 --> 00:01:47,759
Well, I didn't mean that.

22
00:01:49,870 --> 00:01:51,800
When did she start being like this?

23
00:01:52,759 --> 00:01:54,310
Ever since she got pregnant,

24
00:01:54,310 --> 00:01:56,400
she often complained about being tired,

25
00:01:56,400 --> 00:01:58,039
losing hair, and getting acne.

26
00:01:58,039 --> 00:02:00,170
It's been about seven or eight months.

27
00:02:00,950 --> 00:02:01,640
Could it...

28
00:02:01,950 --> 00:02:03,810
Could it be because of this child?

29
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:06,480
Is it that a Heavenly Maiden
can't get pregnant

30
00:02:06,480 --> 00:02:08,410
and starts decaying once she does?

31
00:02:09,190 --> 00:02:09,870
No, no.

32
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:11,860
I'm the one who made her like this.

33
00:02:11,960 --> 00:02:13,160
Don't talk nonsense.

34
00:02:13,400 --> 00:02:14,960
What basis do you have to say that?

35
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:16,150
I... I was just guessing.

36
00:02:16,150 --> 00:02:17,150
Wait. Didn't you

37
00:02:17,170 --> 00:02:18,170
say it first?

38
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:18,590
Come on.

39
00:02:18,590 --> 00:02:20,030
Why are you blaming me?

40
00:02:20,120 --> 00:02:21,680
Honey!

41
00:02:21,840 --> 00:02:23,710
Do you know any gods

42
00:02:23,750 --> 00:02:24,810
who know medicine?

43
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:26,180
The hospitals here

44
00:02:26,310 --> 00:02:27,430
can't cure the Heavenly Maiden's illness.

45
00:02:27,430 --> 00:02:28,470
Help us find one.

46
00:02:28,910 --> 00:02:30,520
I... I think...

47
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:32,260
Well...

48
00:02:32,710 --> 00:02:33,310
Come here.

49
00:02:35,520 --> 00:02:37,120
Take it seriously, Earth God.

50
00:02:37,120 --> 00:02:37,870
Usually, when you can't deal with

51
00:02:37,870 --> 00:02:38,630
a demon,

52
00:02:38,650 --> 00:02:39,910
aren't I the one who helps you?

53
00:02:39,910 --> 00:02:40,970
Yes, that's right.

54
00:02:41,630 --> 00:02:43,490
Well then... I'll try to find one.

55
00:02:50,770 --> 00:02:51,500
My Lord.

56
00:02:52,800 --> 00:02:54,800
How is my wife?

57
00:02:55,430 --> 00:02:56,079
My Lord,

58
00:02:56,710 --> 00:02:57,630
can you tell?

59
00:02:58,750 --> 00:03:00,120
The Five Declines.

60
00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:01,400
I'm afraid

61
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:03,430
she is beyond cure.

62
00:03:05,030 --> 00:03:05,520
My Lord.

63
00:03:06,470 --> 00:03:08,000
Do you have any magic potion

64
00:03:08,080 --> 00:03:08,750
to give us?

65
00:03:10,590 --> 00:03:11,320
Then tell me,

66
00:03:11,680 --> 00:03:12,960
what magic potions do you think there are?

67
00:03:12,960 --> 00:03:14,030
Like that Lingzhi herb or something

68
00:03:14,030 --> 00:03:15,120
the White Snake Demon stole

69
00:03:15,120 --> 00:03:16,650
when she was saving Xu Xian.

70
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:18,120
White Snake Demon?

71
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:21,960
My apologies.

72
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:23,400
I didn't realize your true form

73
00:03:23,400 --> 00:03:24,520
is also a white snake.

74
00:03:24,520 --> 00:03:26,360
My apologies, My Lord. I'm sorry.

75
00:03:26,360 --> 00:03:28,490
You actually believe the storybooks?

76
00:03:30,150 --> 00:03:30,750
Besides,

77
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:33,150
Xu Xian was a mortal,

78
00:03:33,520 --> 00:03:34,960
so a magic potion could save him.

79
00:03:34,960 --> 00:03:35,690
This one here

80
00:03:35,800 --> 00:03:36,680
is an immortal.

81
00:03:37,470 --> 00:03:38,360
Magic potions

82
00:03:40,910 --> 00:03:41,970
are useless to her.

83
00:03:42,430 --> 00:03:43,960
Honey!

84
00:03:43,980 --> 00:03:46,079
It's all my fault!

85
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:49,000
What did he do?

86
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:51,050
I shouldn't have gotten you pregnant!

87
00:03:51,050 --> 00:03:52,590
It must be the pregnancy

88
00:03:52,610 --> 00:03:53,940
that made you like this!

89
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:55,400
You said it.

90
00:03:55,870 --> 00:03:57,310
You said that if a Heavenly Maiden
gets pregnant,

91
00:03:57,310 --> 00:03:58,630
she will become a mortal.

92
00:03:58,630 --> 00:04:00,030
But I really didn't expect

93
00:04:00,030 --> 00:04:01,520
it to be like this.

94
00:04:02,560 --> 00:04:04,400
Pregnancy won't cause a Heavenly Maiden

95
00:04:04,400 --> 00:04:06,200
to go through the Five Declines.

96
00:04:07,470 --> 00:04:08,200
Are you sure?

97
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:09,820
Do you know better than me?

98
00:04:09,840 --> 00:04:10,560
I don't.

99
00:04:11,560 --> 00:04:12,770
Pregnancy will indeed

100
00:04:12,770 --> 00:04:15,430
cause a Heavenly Maiden
to lose some divine power.

101
00:04:15,430 --> 00:04:17,680
But she definitely
won't lose all her power.

102
00:04:17,680 --> 00:04:18,560
She only loses

103
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:20,070
a small portion,

104
00:04:20,829 --> 00:04:22,960
and it gets passed on to the offspring.

105
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:25,120
What if that child

106
00:04:25,430 --> 00:04:28,270
is extremely greedy?

107
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:30,000
You mean

108
00:04:30,270 --> 00:04:31,690
the child in her womb

109
00:04:31,870 --> 00:04:33,330
is draining her lifespan,

110
00:04:33,630 --> 00:04:34,870
causing the Five Declines?

111
00:04:34,870 --> 00:04:35,830
Is it possible?

112
00:04:36,159 --> 00:04:36,890
Impossible!

113
00:04:37,190 --> 00:04:39,050
This... this is Ya and my child.

114
00:04:39,170 --> 00:04:39,830
He wouldn't harm

115
00:04:39,830 --> 00:04:40,690
his own mother.

116
00:04:58,680 --> 00:04:59,830
This child...

117
00:05:00,950 --> 00:05:02,310
isn't showing any movement

118
00:05:02,310 --> 00:05:03,310
or signs of life.

119
00:05:04,270 --> 00:05:05,680
Could it be a stillbirth?

120
00:05:06,360 --> 00:05:07,570
That's you!

121
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:09,260
That's your whole family!

122
00:05:10,120 --> 00:05:10,600
Dongqing!

123
00:05:10,600 --> 00:05:11,620
You damn snake!

124
00:05:11,730 --> 00:05:13,000
I'll make you into a belt!

125
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:13,600
Dongqing!

126
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:15,250
How dare you eat my bananas?

127
00:05:15,270 --> 00:05:16,310
You're disgusting!

128
00:05:16,310 --> 00:05:16,680
I...

129
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:19,060
-Dongqing!
-Disgusting!

130
00:05:22,120 --> 00:05:22,750
Dongqing!

131
00:05:47,630 --> 00:05:50,030
You're really good to the Heavenly Maiden.

132
00:05:50,600 --> 00:05:52,530
You even take care of her yourself.

133
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:53,630
Because

134
00:05:54,600 --> 00:05:55,680
I like her.

135
00:05:56,790 --> 00:05:57,400
Besides,

136
00:05:57,430 --> 00:05:59,120
she is the mother of my child.

137
00:05:59,800 --> 00:06:01,530
I should treat her even better.

138
00:06:01,870 --> 00:06:02,670
You know what?

139
00:06:03,630 --> 00:06:04,720
That baby...

140
00:06:06,040 --> 00:06:07,100
kicked me just now.

141
00:06:07,750 --> 00:06:08,480
But...

142
00:06:08,990 --> 00:06:11,240
you're quite ruthless
to the Heavenly Maiden.

143
00:06:11,240 --> 00:06:12,900
You gave her the deadly poison

144
00:06:13,190 --> 00:06:13,950
through me.

145
00:06:20,430 --> 00:06:22,090
When an immortal gives birth,

146
00:06:22,680 --> 00:06:23,480
the child

147
00:06:23,970 --> 00:06:25,330
absorbs a part

148
00:06:25,360 --> 00:06:27,020
of the mother's divine power.

149
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:29,070
But that's not enough.

150
00:06:29,830 --> 00:06:31,600
So I used demonic power

151
00:06:31,720 --> 00:06:32,850
to make a poison pill

152
00:06:33,560 --> 00:06:34,560
for her to take.

153
00:06:35,390 --> 00:06:37,480
Only when demonic power enters her body

154
00:06:37,480 --> 00:06:38,940
can it stimulate the fetus

155
00:06:38,950 --> 00:06:40,680
to absorb all her divine power.

156
00:06:42,310 --> 00:06:43,120
It's just that

157
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:47,040
I didn't expect

158
00:06:47,800 --> 00:06:48,720
this child

159
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:51,000
would drain

160
00:06:51,230 --> 00:06:52,550
all of her lifespan.

161
00:06:54,270 --> 00:06:55,000
So

162
00:06:55,890 --> 00:06:57,030
I'm willing to preserve this Kunlun

163
00:06:57,030 --> 00:06:58,220
forever for Ya.

164
00:06:59,070 --> 00:07:01,510
Her physical body is completely exhausted.

165
00:07:01,510 --> 00:07:03,270
She will live here forever,

166
00:07:04,070 --> 00:07:04,800
never aging,

167
00:07:05,190 --> 00:07:05,920
never dying,

168
00:07:06,600 --> 00:07:08,190
with eternal life.

169
00:07:08,870 --> 00:07:10,120
So do I need to stay here?

170
00:07:10,120 --> 00:07:10,510
No.

171
00:07:10,680 --> 00:07:12,740
Just come to see her from time to time.

172
00:07:12,950 --> 00:07:13,680
I see.

173
00:07:21,750 --> 00:07:22,510
Remember,

174
00:07:23,800 --> 00:07:25,360
hide your face well.

175
00:07:26,600 --> 00:07:28,330
Make sure she doesn't find out.

176
00:07:34,890 --> 00:07:35,970
I'm still worried

177
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:37,659
that if this model Fei created

178
00:07:37,680 --> 00:07:39,340
turns a thought into reality,

179
00:07:40,790 --> 00:07:42,450
her divine power will return.

180
00:07:42,750 --> 00:07:43,390
But...

181
00:07:44,340 --> 00:07:45,750
if she stays here all the time,

182
00:07:45,750 --> 00:07:47,950
she'll get suspicious sooner or later.

183
00:07:49,680 --> 00:07:50,720
By that time,

184
00:07:51,600 --> 00:07:53,159
I will have become a god.

185
00:07:53,750 --> 00:07:54,680
Tomorrow,

186
00:07:56,120 --> 00:07:57,310
or maybe tonight,

187
00:07:57,720 --> 00:07:58,980
the child will be born.

188
00:07:59,510 --> 00:08:01,120
In this world model,

189
00:08:01,830 --> 00:08:03,800
I possess endless demonic power.

190
00:08:04,630 --> 00:08:07,160
Combined with the divine power
of the child of an immortal,

191
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:08,600
with a mere thought,

192
00:08:10,190 --> 00:08:12,310
I can create infinite worlds.

193
00:08:13,750 --> 00:08:15,360
I can also merge all worlds

194
00:08:15,390 --> 00:08:16,600
into one.

195
00:08:17,070 --> 00:08:17,800
And I

196
00:08:18,950 --> 00:08:21,680
will be the sole ruler.

197
00:08:34,390 --> 00:08:35,320
Eat a little.

198
00:08:37,200 --> 00:08:39,080
My wife is carrying my child.

199
00:08:41,840 --> 00:08:43,240
She is in this condition.

200
00:08:45,870 --> 00:08:47,480
How can I eat?

201
00:08:49,630 --> 00:08:50,760
You said it yourself

202
00:08:50,910 --> 00:08:52,110
that she is like this.

203
00:08:53,910 --> 00:08:55,080
If you don't eat

204
00:08:55,160 --> 00:08:56,360
and ruin your health,

205
00:08:56,360 --> 00:08:57,760
who will take care of her?

206
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:01,910
Before Ya met me,

207
00:09:04,630 --> 00:09:05,960
she was a noble,

208
00:09:07,550 --> 00:09:08,320
beautiful,

209
00:09:10,670 --> 00:09:12,330
inviolable Heavenly Maiden.

210
00:09:15,630 --> 00:09:16,670
But now,

211
00:09:18,080 --> 00:09:19,600
she is lying here.

212
00:09:24,440 --> 00:09:25,320
And I...

213
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:28,600
I'm just a useless mortal!

214
00:09:29,030 --> 00:09:29,320
I...

215
00:09:29,480 --> 00:09:31,550
I can't do anything!

216
00:09:34,380 --> 00:09:35,030
Dongqing!

217
00:09:38,000 --> 00:09:38,620
Dongqing?

218
00:09:39,480 --> 00:09:40,150
Dongqing!

219
00:10:12,120 --> 00:10:13,030
Little bird?

220
00:10:17,550 --> 00:10:18,150
Director!

221
00:10:19,150 --> 00:10:20,580
Are you a Heavenly Maiden too?

222
00:10:20,580 --> 00:10:21,220
Director,

223
00:10:21,630 --> 00:10:22,510
don't you remember me?

224
00:10:22,510 --> 00:10:23,310
I am Wang Fang.

225
00:10:24,080 --> 00:10:25,030
Yan Yuzhen turned me into

226
00:10:25,030 --> 00:10:25,750
a cyber bird

227
00:10:26,200 --> 00:10:26,870
and erased my existence

228
00:10:26,870 --> 00:10:28,030
in the real world.

229
00:10:29,390 --> 00:10:30,320
Yan Yuzhen...

230
00:10:31,150 --> 00:10:32,480
erased your existence?

231
00:10:33,030 --> 00:10:34,090
You know me.

232
00:10:34,510 --> 00:10:36,110
I also work at Xinghuo Media.

233
00:10:36,360 --> 00:10:37,170
You are my superior,

234
00:10:37,170 --> 00:10:39,030
and you've always been good to me.

235
00:10:39,440 --> 00:10:40,040
Director,

236
00:10:40,390 --> 00:10:41,870
you must believe my words.

237
00:10:48,120 --> 00:10:50,440
Director, you've been deceived
by Yan Yuzhen.

238
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:52,030
What did she deceive me about?

239
00:10:52,030 --> 00:10:53,440
This is not the real Kunlun.

240
00:10:53,440 --> 00:10:54,120
It is an AI-created

241
00:10:54,120 --> 00:10:55,200
cyber world.

242
00:10:55,440 --> 00:10:56,510
Yan Yuzhen extracted your consciousness

243
00:10:56,510 --> 00:10:57,600
from your body

244
00:10:57,620 --> 00:10:58,480
and put it here.

245
00:10:58,510 --> 00:10:59,220
She wants you to

246
00:10:59,220 --> 00:10:59,890
give birth here.

247
00:10:59,890 --> 00:11:00,560
This child

248
00:11:00,670 --> 00:11:02,030
will be born in the form of consciousness.

249
00:11:02,030 --> 00:11:03,030
His consciousness will be forever

250
00:11:03,030 --> 00:11:03,910
trapped in the cyber world,

251
00:11:03,910 --> 00:11:05,040
serving Yan Yuzhen!

252
00:11:05,320 --> 00:11:05,840
Your physical body

253
00:11:05,840 --> 00:11:07,000
is still in the real world,

254
00:11:07,000 --> 00:11:09,120
going through Five Declines
and lying on a hospital bed!

255
00:11:09,120 --> 00:11:10,850
Wait. You're talking too fast.

256
00:11:10,960 --> 00:11:12,240
Get out of here quickly!

257
00:11:12,240 --> 00:11:13,600
If you give birth here,

258
00:11:14,030 --> 00:11:16,030
both you and your child
will die in the real world!

259
00:11:16,030 --> 00:11:16,980
Your husband, Xia Dongqing,

260
00:11:16,980 --> 00:11:19,110
is still waiting by your hospital bed.

261
00:11:19,120 --> 00:11:19,720
Dongqing?

262
00:11:19,960 --> 00:11:20,360
He...

263
00:11:26,080 --> 00:11:26,680
Dongqing?

264
00:11:26,910 --> 00:11:27,510
Director,

265
00:11:27,630 --> 00:11:28,690
he's not Dongqing.

266
00:11:28,750 --> 00:11:29,550
Look closely.

267
00:11:29,720 --> 00:11:30,810
His face is fake!

268
00:11:31,240 --> 00:11:32,640
He is Yuanji in disguise!

269
00:11:44,510 --> 00:11:45,240
Yuanji?

270
00:11:45,750 --> 00:11:46,390
Wang Fang,

271
00:11:47,130 --> 00:11:48,080
you traitor!

272
00:11:48,630 --> 00:11:49,690
You deserve to die.

273
00:12:05,440 --> 00:12:06,720
Noisy bird.

274
00:12:07,000 --> 00:12:08,390
It messed up my floor.

275
00:12:17,440 --> 00:12:18,360
Yan Yuzhen!

276
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:19,750
You lied to me!

277
00:12:20,790 --> 00:12:21,850
This is not Kunlun!

278
00:12:22,200 --> 00:12:23,790
This is Kunlun.

279
00:12:24,150 --> 00:12:24,600
Ya,

280
00:12:25,030 --> 00:12:26,270
I'm your friend.

281
00:12:26,390 --> 00:12:27,990
Why do you believe that bird?

282
00:12:28,000 --> 00:12:29,670
You don't even know that woman.

283
00:12:29,670 --> 00:12:30,870
She said she knows me.

284
00:12:31,670 --> 00:12:32,400
She also said

285
00:12:32,750 --> 00:12:33,320
you erased

286
00:12:33,320 --> 00:12:34,780
her existence in reality.

287
00:12:35,510 --> 00:12:37,080
She is just a demon,

288
00:12:37,440 --> 00:12:38,510
good at lying.

289
00:12:38,790 --> 00:12:39,390
I don't know

290
00:12:39,390 --> 00:12:40,850
how she ended up in Kunlun.

291
00:12:42,240 --> 00:12:43,270
Trust me.

292
00:12:44,080 --> 00:12:45,080
Then what about him?

293
00:12:45,080 --> 00:12:46,720
Why did he pretend to be Dongqing?

294
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:47,920
Aren't you pregnant?

295
00:12:48,630 --> 00:12:50,150
You'll give birth in a couple of days.

296
00:12:50,150 --> 00:12:51,880
Dongqing can't come to Kunlun.

297
00:12:52,150 --> 00:12:53,910
I was afraid you'd miss him too much,

298
00:12:53,910 --> 00:12:55,440
so I turned Yuanji

299
00:12:55,480 --> 00:12:56,550
into Dongqing.

300
00:12:57,030 --> 00:12:58,890
If Dongqing can't come to Kunlun,

301
00:12:59,720 --> 00:13:00,870
why can he?

302
00:13:01,200 --> 00:13:02,670
And why are you here too?

303
00:13:02,840 --> 00:13:03,510
I...

304
00:13:05,150 --> 00:13:06,150
If this is Kunlun,

305
00:13:06,750 --> 00:13:07,480
besides me,

306
00:13:08,790 --> 00:13:09,600
are you two

307
00:13:10,750 --> 00:13:12,550
the only ones here now?

308
00:13:19,270 --> 00:13:21,400
Where are the other Heavenly Maidens?

309
00:13:22,440 --> 00:13:23,640
Where are my sisters?

310
00:13:26,060 --> 00:13:27,660
Why aren't they in Kunlun?

311
00:13:29,870 --> 00:13:30,800
What's going on?

312
00:13:31,360 --> 00:13:32,110
It's not me.

313
00:13:43,360 --> 00:13:44,240
Yan Yuzhen!

314
00:13:45,630 --> 00:13:47,150
You brought me here!

315
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:50,400
You said this was Kunlun.

316
00:13:53,150 --> 00:13:54,870
You deceived a Heavenly Maiden

317
00:13:54,870 --> 00:13:56,000
and forged Kunlun.

318
00:13:56,030 --> 00:13:57,240
How dare you!

319
00:14:00,070 --> 00:14:02,450
If this is really Kunlun,

320
00:14:03,040 --> 00:14:04,520
then I should have

321
00:14:04,550 --> 00:14:05,750
all my divine power.

322
00:14:06,600 --> 00:14:07,030
Oh no.

323
00:14:07,630 --> 00:14:08,670
She's going to use her divine power.

324
00:14:08,670 --> 00:14:09,330
Against us.

325
00:14:09,840 --> 00:14:10,870
Yan Yuzhen!

326
00:14:11,600 --> 00:14:12,600
Let me out!

327
00:14:24,630 --> 00:14:25,150
Yuanji!

328
00:14:34,200 --> 00:14:35,260
You killed Yuanji.

329
00:14:35,750 --> 00:14:37,210
He was just a 2D character.

330
00:14:37,840 --> 00:14:38,750
He shouldn't even have existed

331
00:14:38,750 --> 00:14:39,670
in this world.

332
00:14:40,390 --> 00:14:41,590
The same goes for you.

333
00:14:43,360 --> 00:14:44,690
You won't let me go back.

334
00:14:46,080 --> 00:14:47,120
If you die,

335
00:14:48,200 --> 00:14:49,600
can I go back then?

336
00:14:49,910 --> 00:14:50,840
No! No!

337
00:14:51,240 --> 00:14:51,670
Ya!

338
00:14:52,600 --> 00:14:53,720
I did it all for you!

339
00:14:53,860 --> 00:14:54,720
You are no longer a Heavenly Maiden.

340
00:14:54,720 --> 00:14:55,850
Have you forgotten?

341
00:14:57,120 --> 00:14:59,050
I'm not a Heavenly Maiden anymore?

342
00:15:00,150 --> 00:15:01,280
Have you forgotten?

343
00:15:02,720 --> 00:15:03,960
You are pregnant.

344
00:15:04,630 --> 00:15:06,830
You're carrying Xia Dongqing's child.

345
00:15:06,850 --> 00:15:07,480
Now that you're pregnant,

346
00:15:07,480 --> 00:15:09,480
you're no longer a Heavenly Maiden.

347
00:15:09,720 --> 00:15:11,030
As a mother,

348
00:15:11,510 --> 00:15:13,120
you have to pay the price.

349
00:15:13,870 --> 00:15:15,360
You have become a mortal

350
00:15:15,670 --> 00:15:17,510
without divine power.

351
00:15:23,320 --> 00:15:24,440
A mortal?

352
00:15:31,270 --> 00:15:31,840
Ya.

353
00:15:33,240 --> 00:15:34,360
I brought you here

354
00:15:34,440 --> 00:15:35,670
with absolutely no ill intent.

355
00:15:35,670 --> 00:15:36,800
Don't you remember?

356
00:15:38,320 --> 00:15:40,320
Hair loss, breakouts,

357
00:15:40,840 --> 00:15:41,750
weakness.

358
00:15:42,240 --> 00:15:43,100
And finally...

359
00:15:44,120 --> 00:15:45,120
aging overnight.

360
00:15:46,240 --> 00:15:46,870
I am...

361
00:15:48,510 --> 00:15:50,370
going through the Five Declines?

362
00:15:53,200 --> 00:15:54,480
In my world,

363
00:15:55,030 --> 00:15:56,890
you can escape the Five Declines.

364
00:15:57,550 --> 00:15:58,960
And you can escape death

365
00:15:59,200 --> 00:16:00,870
and all the terrifying things

366
00:16:00,910 --> 00:16:01,960
in the real world.

367
00:16:11,320 --> 00:16:12,670
I lied to you,

368
00:16:13,270 --> 00:16:15,030
but it was for your own good.

369
00:16:20,390 --> 00:16:21,360
I even

370
00:16:22,120 --> 00:16:24,870
created a Kunlun for you.

371
00:16:26,550 --> 00:16:27,510
I remember now.

372
00:16:30,480 --> 00:16:31,150
Perhaps

373
00:16:32,390 --> 00:16:33,590
I misunderstood you.

374
00:16:39,030 --> 00:16:39,790
It hurts!

375
00:16:40,390 --> 00:16:41,190
What's wrong?

376
00:16:41,670 --> 00:16:42,360
Is this...

377
00:16:43,120 --> 00:16:44,030
a contraction?

378
00:16:44,240 --> 00:16:45,750
The baby is coming.

379
00:16:50,000 --> 00:16:50,930
Don't be afraid.

380
00:16:51,120 --> 00:16:52,120
I'm here.

381
00:16:52,630 --> 00:16:55,960
I will take good care of you

382
00:16:56,840 --> 00:16:58,550
and your child.
